snippet.title: WINCH IT OUT - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
*WINCH IT OUT* is a Hardcore, Physics-based, Driving Platformer. If you're tired of the same old Gas-and-Go 2D Racing games and want a more *Challenging* experience, This one is for you.

Available on Google Play (Android) and Steam (PC/Linux/Mac)

Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.araslanix.winchitoutfull
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2956360/WINCH_IT_OUT/

Visit: https://impress.games/press-kit/araslanix/winch-it-out
For the Presskit
